CD Tray: Play your audio CDs directly from the system tray
(c) 2012 Alfonso Saavedra "Son Link"
http://sonlinkblog.blogspot.com/p/cd-tray.html
Under GPLv3 License
 
To install execute (as root user) the script "install.sh"
 
Command line parameters:
-d | --device <device>: set the device to read the CD from (usualy /dev/sr0 or /dev/cdrom)
-f | --force : if another cdtray instance is running, kill it and start a new one
